    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <ul>
	<li><b>Scope:</b> Implement a service triggered by the <tt>ContributionSubmission</tt> event. It must fetch the Coordinator's email for the student's faculty and send a notification.</li>
	<li><b>Acceptance Criteria:</b> Emails contain a direct link to the contribution. Logic includes a "Retry" mechanism if the SMTP server is temporarily down.</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

