    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <ul>
	<li><b>Scope:</b> Create {{POST /api/contributions/
{id}
<p>/comments}}. Implement logic to ensure only one "Official Comment" can be made by the Coordinator, but allow for a "Chat-like" interaction if required.</p></li>
	<li><b>Acceptance Criteria:</b> Successfully saves comments to the DB and links them to the <tt>CoordinatorID</tt>. Returns $403\text
{ Forbidden}
<p>$ if a Coordinator tries to comment on a student from a different faculty.</p></li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
